  "title": "AMBULANCE DRIVER | MEDICAL TRANSPORT OPERATOR (MTO)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Applicant preferably with more than three years of experience</li>\n  <li>Assist with transferring Patients from and to hospitals, homes, nursing homes, and dialysis centres.</li>\n  <li>Assist the Medical Assistants in transferring patients on wheelchairs or medical stretchers.</li>\n  <li>To be service-oriented, as we are a healthcare provider and frequently deal with the elderly or those with disabilities.</li>\n  <li>As MTOs, we require you to be physically fit.</li>\n  <li>You should not have any outstanding traffic offences or pending court cases (clean record preferred).</li>\n</ul>",
