    "description": "<p>I.M. Ambulance Services (IMA) was established in 2012. We have been providing Medical Transport Services (MTS) for almost a decade. We also provide Emergency Ambulance Services for all high dependency cases and event coverages. With trained professionals in our crew, we believe in providing only the best in the business.</p>\n<p>I.M. Ambulance Services at your disposal 24 Hours A Day, 365 Days round the clock.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We currently own a fleet of 20 Ambulances that are all adequately equipped to provide maximum safety and comfort during transportation. They can also accommodate patients varying from different sizes, weight and well as accessibility needs.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Our teams are all well-trained to provide patients with safe and reliable transfer services from or to home, hospitals as well as Nursing Homes and Dialysis Centers..</p>",
